-- Chinese and German Governments, Companies Sign 10 Deals During Merkel Trip
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-16T04:20:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-16/chinese-and-german-governments-companies-sign-10-deals-during-merkel-trip.html

          
          
             The Chinese and German governments
and companies of the two countries signed 10 agreements during
the visit to China of German Chancellor Angela Merkel, the
Xinhua News Agency reported.  
 The agreements include those on finance, truck production,
economic and technological cooperation, climate and
environmental protection and export lending, Xinhua reported.  
          
          


  


        